          "rangeEnd": 55532,
          "markText": "侍卫亲军中的叛军开始逼迫李嗣源在黄河以北地区称帝，而把黄河以南地区的统治权留给庄宗。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1777455844,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-04-29 17:44:04",
          "chapterUid": 12,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300040966&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=55490&rangeEnd=55532",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/35332a00813ab7680g016439?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=55490&rangeEnd=55532"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300040966_12_54404-54459",
          "range": "54404-54459",
          "rangeStart": 54404,
          "rangeEnd": 54459,
          "markText": "三月初六，李嗣源以惊人的速度到达魏州，然而皇帝的这些侍卫亲军——被认为是最忠诚于皇帝的军队也在短时间内哗变了。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1777455724,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-04-29 17:42:04",
          "chapterUid": 12,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300040966&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=54404&rangeEnd=54459",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/35332a00813ab7680g016439?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=54404&rangeEnd=54459"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300040966_12_47789-47844",
          "range": "47789-47844",
          "rangeStart": 47789,
          "rangeEnd": 47844,
          "markText": "贝州乱兵连续逼迫两位将校当他们的首领，但都没有成功，他们杀掉二人，并且提着他们的首级来到赵在礼面前，逼其就范。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1777455445,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-04-29 17:37:25",
          "chapterUid": 12,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300040966&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=47789&rangeEnd=47844",
